dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This geodatabase feature class contains line features for each road centerline within Eau Claire County, WI. The data functions as a critical component of the E911 dispatch system as well as a base layer for geographic analysis and mapping. The data is maintained jointly by Eau Claire County and the City of Eau Claire.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
